data.meta_description: Tomas Bartomeus profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
Tomas Bartomeus is 41 years old (Oct 27, 1982), 174 cm tall and plays for Guaireña.

Tomas Bartomeus prefers to play with right foot. His jersey number is 14.

If Tomas Bartomeus is going to be in Guaireña lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Tomas Bartomeus plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Tomas Bartomeus football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Tomas Bartomeus played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
